{"tid":730303,"cid":15,"subCid":0,"title":"[儲首期買樓] 大家返工帶飯會點樣設計最平既一餐lunch同時有足夠營養, 窮撚要買樓!","createTime":"2018-07-05T09:42:45.000Z","updateTime":"2018-08-04T05:08:10.000Z","uid":127929,"like":20,"dislike":42,"uniUserReply":53,"replies":[{"pid":"8adfddecdad945d14e1cde1a872ba102fed2f29c","tid":730303,"uid":127929,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-07-05T09:42:45.000Z","msg":"窮撚平時出去一餐lunch：$70<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/22.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n目標係要5年內儲首期買樓<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/23.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n以下係我既計劃：<br />\n<br />\n (一杯米185g + 茄汁焗豆220g/豆腐350g +一杯 Whey朱奶 + 一粒善存) <br />\n<br />\n= $82.9/(8kg/185g) + $10 + $475/(2.27kg/32g) +  319/150 = <span style=\"color: red;\">$20</span><br />\n<br />\n每月足足慳到 = ($70-$20)*30日 = $1500<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/08.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n如果計埋晚餐都係咁足足慳到 = ($100-$20)*30 +$1500 = $3900<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/06.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n其它開支再cut一cut, 過多幾年好快買到樓<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/29.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/29.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/29.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n利申：月入22k 窮撚, 目標月入80%以上用黎儲錢買樓<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/11.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"7a53595e1ea45c464cfb8792d8c40c17e663b7d1","tid":730303,"uid":127929,"like":9,"dislike":2,"score":7,"citedBy":3,"replyTime":"2018-07-05T09:43:38.000Z","msg":"早餐已cut, 一日兩餐only<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/33.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n有冇人跟隊一齊黎個買樓夢<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/26.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"640c6bd7c0c16bc39db5590f051f6022d9a7b247","tid":730303,"uid":52911,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"quote":{"pid":"7a53595e1ea45c464cfb8792d8c40c17e663b7d1","tid":730303,"uid":127929,"like":9,"dislike":2,"score":7,"citedBy":3,"replyTime":"2018-07-05T09:43:38.000Z","msg":"早餐已cut, 一日兩餐only<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/33.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n有冇人跟隊